Class GCMReceiver

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2

    public class GCMReceiver
extends com.google.android.gcm.GCMBaseIntentService
    Class that handles new message received with Google Cloud Messaging.

    It handles the registration of the gcm_id (identifier sent by Google for the device), and synchronizes that identifier to CommonSense. This class also handles commands sent by CommonSense to this device.
    Author:
    Ahmy Yulrizka
